    "description": "Identifying flow modules in ecological networks using Infomap.\n\nNetwork community detection using the Map Equation framework.\n\nA a package for running Infomap, inspired by ecological networks.\n\nInfomap finds important patterns in complex networks by optimizing the map equation, which exploits the information-theoretic duality between the problem of compressing data and detecting patterns.\n\nThis site is an extension of the paper Identifying flow modules in ecological networks using Infomap.",
